sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Service as odh-dashboard Service<br/>8443/TCP
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuthSrv as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access

    User->>Route: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>No auth
    Route->>Service: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS reencrypt
    Service->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS 1.2+

    alt User not authenticated
        OAuth->>User: Redirect to OAuth login
        User->>OAuthSrv: OAuth login flow (HTTPS/443)
        OAuthSrv-->>User: OAuth token
        User->>OAuth: Request with OAuth token
    end

    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate Bearer Token<br/>Check project list permission
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward request (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    Backend->>Backend: Validate token from header
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET resources (HTTPS/443)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Resource data
    Backend-->>OAuth: Response (HTTP/8080)
    OAuth-->>Service: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Service-->>Route: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Route-->>User: HTML/JS Response (HTTPS/443)

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 2: Notebook Creation

    User->>Route: POST /api/notebooks (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>Service: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Service->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: POST /api/notebooks (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CRD (HTTPS/443)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create PVC (HTTPS/443)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: PVC created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (HTTPS/443)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: ConfigMap created
    Backend-->>OAuth: Success response (HTTP/8080)
    OAuth-->>Service: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Service-->>Route: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Route-->>User: JSON Response (HTTPS/443)

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 3: Metrics Query

    User->>Route: GET /api/prometheus (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>Service: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Service->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: GET /api/prometheus (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>Thanos: Query metrics (HTTPS/9092)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Prometheus metrics data
    Backend-->>OAuth: Metrics response (HTTP/8080)
    OAuth-->>Service: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Service-->>Route: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Route-->>User: JSON Response (HTTPS/443)

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 4: Model Registry Integration

    User->>Route: POST /api/modelRegistries (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>Service: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Service->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: POST /api/modelRegistries (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create ModelRegistry CRD (HTTPS/443)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: ModelRegistry created
    Backend->>ModelReg: API call (HTTPS/443)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ModelReg-->>Backend: Model metadata
    Backend-->>OAuth: Success response (HTTP/8080)
    OAuth-->>Service: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Service-->>Route: Response (HTTPS/8443)
    Route-->>User: JSON Response (HTTPS/443)
